This is the code for task 1 to do broadcast using binomial tree.
The source files are in /src
The header files are in /include
The source file for broadcast using binomial tree is log_bcast.cpp
For comparison, the broadcast using simple algorithm is also included, with the source file is simple_bcast.cpp

To compile the code:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..

To run the code:
mpirun -np n ./hw5_task1
